ce\": \"In the space of seven days, she won two bronze medals in the 5,000 metres, having also run a heat and the 10,000-metre, and a spectacular gold in the marathon when she outsprinted Ethiopia's then world record holder Tigist Assefa to win by just three seconds.\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 678, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999999997160103, \"rank\": 2.8394479310092335e-10, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}, {\"begin\": 714, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tigist_Assefa\", \"score\": 0.9999999943293005, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tigist Assefa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tigist_Assefa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tigist_Assefa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 510}, {\"ngram\": \"seven days\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"two bronze medals\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 551}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5,000 metres\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"a heat\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10,000-metre\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the marathon\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"just three seconds\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never thought I was going to win this one,\\\" said Hassan after receiving her award in Monaco on Sunday.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hassan_district\", \"score\": 0.8174842849773257, \"rank\": 0.18204025654524117, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hassan_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hassan_district\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"